---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Button from "../../components/Button/Button.astro";
import aiHeroImage from "../../assets/ai-grading-dashboard-grid.png";
import aiConceptImage from "../../assets/ai-grading-lab-workflow.png";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="AI Roadmap | EmbryoOne AI"
  description="Explore EmbryoOne's AI roadmap from embryo grading foundation to predictive IVF decision intelligence."
>
  <section class="page-section bg-white">
    <div class="page-container grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow text-[#6C3CF0]">AI Roadmap</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-tebra-teal-dark sm:text-5xl">
          Building the future of IVF intelligence
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-base text-gray-600 sm:text-lg">
          EmbryoOne AI is evolving beyond grading toward predictive insights, smarter workflows, and
          outcome-driven decision support across the IVF cycle.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-[#5A4C72]">From observation to intelligence to prediction.</p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <Button href="/demo" label="Book a demo" variant="primary" size="md" />
          <Button href="/contact" label="Join early access" variant="secondary" size="md" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <img
        src={aiHeroImage.src}
        alt="AI roadmap hero visual showing connected embryo intelligence interfaces"
        class="w-full rounded-3xl border border-[#E9DDFB] shadow-[0_24px_48px_-36px_rgba(108,60,240,0.5)]"
        loading="eager"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section bg-[#F7F1FF]">
    <div class="page-container">
      <h2 class="heading-md text-center text-tebra-teal-dark">Where we're headed</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-4xl text-center text-base text-gray-700">
        Today, AI helps standardize embryo grading. Tomorrow, it will help predict outcomes,
        optimize decisions, and guide the entire IVF journey.
      </p>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-4xl text-center text-base text-gray-700">
        Our roadmap is focused on turning data into actionable intelligence without removing
        clinical control.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-[#51285f]">
    <div class="page-container">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white sm:text-4xl">Be part of what's next</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-200">
          Join early access programs and help shape the future of IVF intelligence.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
          <Button href="/contact" label="Join early access" variant="primary" size="md" />
          <Button href="/demo" label="Talk to our team" variant="outline-light" size="md" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section bg-white">
    <div class="page-container">
      <h2 class="heading-md text-center text-tebra-teal-dark">AI roadmap timeline</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-center text-base text-gray-600">
        Clear phase-by-phase evolution from standardized grading to full clinical decision intelligence.
      </p>

      <ol class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-6xl space-y-6">
        <li class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[160px_minmax(0,1fr)] md:gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:flex-col md:gap-2">
            <span class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-full bg-tebra-teal px-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">Phase 1</span>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">Foundation (Current)</p>
          </div>
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-[#EADDFD] bg-[#FAF7FF] p-5 md:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">Standardized embryo intelligence</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              We've built a strong foundation for consistent, objective embryo assessment across labs.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">AI-based embryo grading</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Morphology classification</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Confidence scoring</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Image-based detection</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[160px_minmax(0,1fr)] md:gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:flex-col md:gap-2">
            <span class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-full bg-tebra-teal px-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">Phase 2</span>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">Enhanced Analysis (Near Term)</p>
          </div>
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-[#EADDFD] bg-[#FAF7FF] p-5 md:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">Deeper image understanding</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Moving from single-image evaluation to richer, context-aware analysis.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Multi-image / batch analysis</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Improved grading accuracy</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Enhanced morphology detection</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Workflow automation improvements</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[160px_minmax(0,1fr)] md:gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:flex-col md:gap-2">
            <span class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-full bg-tebra-teal px-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">Phase 3</span>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">Time-Lapse Intelligence</p>
          </div>
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-[#EADDFD] bg-[#FAF7FF] p-5 md:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">Understanding embryo development over time</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Analyze how embryos evolve not just how they look at a single point in time.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Time-lapse embryo tracking</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Morphokinetic analysis</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Development pattern recognition</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Progression trend visualization</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[160px_minmax(0,1fr)] md:gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:flex-col md:gap-2">
            <span class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-full bg-tebra-teal px-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">Phase 4</span>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">Predictive Modeling</p>
          </div>
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-[#EADDFD] bg-[#FAF7FF] p-5 md:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">From grading to prediction</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">AI begins to support outcome-based decisions not just classification.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Implantation likelihood prediction</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Outcome probability scoring</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Cycle-level insights</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Risk stratification support</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </li>

        <li class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-[160px_minmax(0,1fr)] md:gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 md:flex-col md:gap-2">
            <span class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-full bg-tebra-teal px-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white">Phase 5</span>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">Decision Intelligence (Future Vision)</p>
          </div>
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-[#EADDFD] bg-[#FAF7FF] p-5 md:p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-tebra-teal-dark">Fully assisted IVF decision support</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">AI becomes a clinical co-pilot supporting every key decision across the IVF journey.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Personalized embryo scoring</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Treatment optimization insights</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">End-to-end cycle intelligence</li>
              <li class="rounded-lg border border-white/60 bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Real-time decision recommendations</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section bg-[#F7F1FF]">
    <div class="page-container grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="heading-md text-tebra-teal-dark">A connected, intelligent IVF ecosystem</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-700">
          A connected, intelligent IVF ecosystem powered by data, guided by clinicians.
        </p>
      </div>
      <img
        src={aiConceptImage.src}
        alt="AI concept visual connecting grading, workflow, and clinical intelligence"
        class="w-full rounded-3xl border border-[#E9DDFB] shadow-[0_20px_40px_-34px_rgba(108,60,240,0.45)]"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section bg-white">
    <div class="page-container">
      <h2 class="heading-md text-center text-tebra-teal-dark">How we build AI</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-center text-base text-gray-700">
        Our roadmap is guided by principles that ensure safety, trust, and clinical relevance.
      </p>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-8 grid max-w-5xl gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#EADDFD] bg-[#FAF7FF] px-5 py-4 text-sm font-medium text-[#51285f]">Clinically grounded — Built for real IVF workflows</div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#EADDFD] bg-[#FAF7FF] px-5 py-4 text-sm font-medium text-[#51285f]">Human-in-the-loop — AI supports, not replaces</div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#EADDFD] bg-[#FAF7FF] px-5 py-4 text-sm font-medium text-[#51285f]">Transparent — Explainable outputs and traceability</div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#EADDFD] bg-[#FAF7FF] px-5 py-4 text-sm font-medium text-[#51285f]">Continuously improving — Learning from real-world data</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section bg-[#F7F1FF]">
    <div class="page-container">
      <h2 class="heading-md text-center text-tebra-teal-dark">Why this evolution matters</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-4xl text-center text-base text-gray-700">
        As IVF becomes more data-driven, labs need tools that go beyond manual interpretation.
        EmbryoOne AI will help teams move faster, reduce uncertainty, and make more informed
        decisions while maintaining full clinical control.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="page-container rounded-3xl bg-tebra-teal-dark px-6 py-10 text-white sm:px-10">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl">See where AI can take your lab</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base text-gray-100">
        Explore EmbryoOne today and be ready for what comes next.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-7">
        <Button href="/demo" label="Book a demo" variant="outline-light" size="md" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
